<div id="nr_title" class="nr_title">382：结局篇：满满都是你的日记</div>
<div id="nr_top" class="nr_page"><table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0"><tbody><tr><td class="prev"><a id="pt_prev" onclick="shuqian(&quot;4733&quot;,&quot;3482383&quot;)"><font>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;存书签</font></a></td><td class="mulu"><a id="pt_mulu" href="/bookcase.aspx">书架管理</a></td><td class="next"><a id="pt_next" href="/chapterlist-4733/">返回目录</a></td></tr></tbody></table></div>
